民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=66da595e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n但係件事未完！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要繼續話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"691e590aa4499cd7c9cefb3997ed47782f10cffc","tid":1840661,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"董伯伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afae49a0d9ddb0c1c695f5977e9d3c5cce24d8c","tid":1840661,"uid":8011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"我諗佢呢番說話係指要放棄留念前英政府，<br />\n要擁抱中國大陸，中國大陸將會成大勢。<br />\n否則你無法同中國大陸文化接軌。"},{"pid":"2fe4dd7b2f3e1d3bc597ae570b066b04d0751970","tid":1840661,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"159556071923609584b4a9890399eecc8cff29e1","tid":1840661,"uid":217757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"83a11610eaf32d67bf6816505bb37742f0c7bf12","tid":1840661,"uid":19586